# .trivyignore
# Documented CVE suppressions — architectural exceptions, not hidden risks.
# Each entry has a justification and an expiration date for annual review.
# Review by: 2027-04-19

# xlsx CVE-2023-30533 (Prototype Pollution) — SUPPRESS
# xlsx CVE-2024-22363 (ReDoS) — SUPPRESS
# Rationale: xlsx is intentionally retained because TPN GL statement parsing
# requires XLSX.SSF.parse_date_code and low-level cell addressing that ExcelJS
# cannot replicate. Risk is mitigated at the API route level (authenticated
# endpoints only, no user-controlled formula execution). See BUILD_22 architecture.
CVE-2023-30533
CVE-2024-22363
